\c 41
\s Munyengetero pakurwara
\d Kumutungamiriri wekuimba. Pisarema raDhavhidhi.
\p
\v 1 Wakaropafadzwa anorangarira murombo\x + Zvir. 14.21. Mat. 5.7.\x*; Jehovha achamununura nezuva rechakaipa\x + Mab. 12.11.\x*.
\v 2 Jehovha achamuchengetedza, nekumuraramisa; achava wakaropafadzwa panyika; uye hamungamukumikidzi kuchido chevavengi vake.
\v 3 Jehovha achamutsigira panhovo yeurwere; muchashandura nhovo yake yose pahosha yake\x + Map. 20.2.\x*.
\p
\v 4 Ini ndakati: Jehovha, ndinzwirei tsitsi\x + Map. 4.1.\x*; poresai mweya wangu; nokuti ndakakutadzirai\x + Map. 6.2.\x*.
\v 5 Vavengi vangu vanotaura kuipa pamusoro pangu \add vachiti\add*: Uchafa rinhi, zita rake rirove?
\v 6 Kunyange kana achiuya kuona, anotaura zvisina maturo; moyo wake unozviunganidzira uipi; anobuda panze, ndokutaura\x + Map. 12.2. 144.8.\x*.
\v 7 Vese vanondivenga vanoita zeve-zeve pamwe chete kundirwisa; vanondirongera zvakaipa kwandiri; \add vachiti\add*:
\v 8 Chinhu chakaipa chakanamatira paari; uye sezvo akarara pasi, haachamukizve\x + 41.3.\x*.
\v 9 Hongu, murume weushamwari hwangu wandaivimba maari\x + Job. 19.19. Map. 55.12,13,20. 2 Sam. 15.12. Jer. 9.4.\x*, aidya chingwa changu, wakandisimudzira chichitsinho\x + Joh. 13.18. Mab. 1.16.\x*.
\p
\v 10 Asi imwi, Jehovha, ndinzwirei tsitsi, mugondisimudzira, kuti ndivatsive\x + Map. 4.1.\x*.
\v 11 Neizvi ndinoziva kuti munofadzwa neni, nokuti muvengi wangu haana kufara pamusoro pangu.
\v 12 Kana ndiri ini, munonditsigira pauchokwadi hwangu; uye munondiisa pamberi penyu kusvika rinhi narinhi\x + Map. 63.8. Map. 17.5.\x*.
\p
\v 13 Ngaarumbidzwe Jehovha, Mwari waIsraeri, kubva pakusingaperi kusvika pakusingaperi\x + Ruk. 1.68.\x*. Ameni, uye Ameni\x + Map. 72.19. 89.52. 106.48. 150.6.\x*.